{"tid":1950193,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"陳雲：驚天大發現！卡介苗有效抑制武漢冠狀病毒。","createTime":"2020-03-30T07:32:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-30T16:23:39.000Z","uid":271829,"like":6,"dislike":113,"uniUserReply":71,"replies":[{"pid":"c6c7dc4379f04591d844b5f92f14a75422538e9d","tid":1950193,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T07:32:54.000Z","msg":"陳雲：驚天大發現！卡介苗有效抑制武漢冠狀病毒。大佬呀，原來我們大家已經早有抗體。澳洲醫學界發現，超過一百年歷史的肺結核疫苗&mdash;&mdash;卡介苗有效抑制新冠狀病毒。而卡介苗是絕大部分兒童都會接種的傳統安全疫苗。<br />\nCovid-19是新病毒，但病癥是舊的傷風感冒，而醫藥是舊的感冒藥、舊的瘧疾藥或曬太陽。至於疫苗，是超過一百年歷史的卡介苗，大家已經接種咗。<br />\n世紀大笑劇，問你服未？<br />\nCentury-Old Vaccine Investigated as a Weapon Against Coronavirus<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2020-03-30/century-old-vaccine-investigated-as-a-weapon-against-coronavirus?fbclid=IwAR0_iybRxylwmhxxv5eSWUYUQ49TytJ6gYnvhsz2ibgDcRyGWvKcEzifiqM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2020-03-30%2Fcentury-old-vaccine-investigated-as-a-weapon-against-coronavirus%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0_iybRxylwmhxxv5eSWUYUQ49TytJ6gYnvhsz2ibgDcRyGWvKcEzifiqM&d=HeGJypC3zV9uypmZg8TJ2RckzRVyZutP2gug%2B5Lqx%2Fc%3D&h=199166b0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2020-03-30/century-old-vaccine-investigated-as-a-weapon-against-coronavirus?fbclid=IwAR0_iybRxylwmhxxv5eSWUYUQ49TytJ6gYnvhsz2ibgDcRyGWvKcEzifiqM</a>"},{"pid":"19655d0fe3e2adbc3f228078368198497e73171f","tid":1950193,"uid":193642,"like":25,"dislike":2,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T07:34:55.000Z","msg":"接種咗都奶野wo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"612d4855a7e873e871cd5bef79ca20363c2f291f","tid":1950193,"uid":141151,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T07:35:14.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">拉</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"bfca6ddb6c31b289e438cefa21aa743cfb52a67c","tid":1950193,"uid":81273,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3