id":15826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T08:17:42.000Z","msg":"國屍真係學貫中西 上知天文下知地理 而家連醫科都可以鳩up兩嘴 點夠你玩呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e78e1c1a67a5ed81a538f0dde9fc3328b936f8f","tid":1950193,"uid":132302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T08:18:43.000Z","msg":"拉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6ae723847df5e53338a83ec0047e000a1ce235e","tid":1950193,"uid":209603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c6c7dc4379f04591d844b5f92f14a75422538e9d","tid":1950193,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T07:32:54.000Z","msg":"陳雲：驚天大發現！卡介苗有效抑制武漢冠狀病毒。大佬呀，原來我們大家已經早有抗體。澳洲醫學界發現，超過一百年歷史的肺結核疫苗&mdash;&mdash;卡介苗有效抑制新冠狀病毒。而卡介苗是絕大部分兒童都會接種的傳統安全疫苗。<br />\nCovid-19是新病毒，但病癥是舊的傷風感冒，而醫藥是舊的感冒藥、舊的瘧疾藥或曬太陽。至於疫苗，是超過一百年歷史的卡介苗，大家已經接種咗。<br />\n世紀大笑劇，問你服未？<br />\nCentury-Old Vaccine Investigated as a Weapon Against Coronavirus<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2020-03-30/century-old-vaccine-investigated-as-a-weapon-against-coronavirus?fbclid=IwAR0_iybRxylwmhxxv5eSWUYUQ49TytJ6gYnvhsz2ibgDcRyGWvKcEzifiqM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2020-03-30%2Fcentury-old-vaccine-investigated-as-a-weapon-against-coronavirus%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0_iybRxylwmhxxv5eSWUYUQ49TytJ6gYnvhsz2ibgDcRyGWvKcEzifiqM&d=HeGJypC3zV9uypmZg8TJ2RckzRVyZutP2gug%2B5Lqx%2Fc%3D&h=199166b0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2020-03-30/century-old-vaccine-investigated-as-a-weapon-against-coronavirus?fbclid=IwAR0_iybRxylwmhxxv5eSWUYUQ49TytJ6gYnvhsz2ibgDcRyGWvKcEzifiqM</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T08:19:03.000Z","msg":"樓主借個位黎置頂可以嗎<br />\n<br />\n要人要錢要資源！線下文宣全港大行動 重建文宣網絡<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/ausnGEU\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/ausnGEU</a>"},{"pid":"cdb7dafca072d080bda91b413129ba20b